52:11.621 --> 52:12.747
Harapan saya.

52:14.123 --> 52:15.333
Talian hayat saya.

52:18.336 --> 52:19.462
Selamat tinggal.

52:20.630 --> 52:22.381
BARBEKU ARANG PIGGY

52:22.465 --> 52:23.466
