apa kata kita ucap selamat?

53:34.954 --> 53:36.664
Helo, Pn. Joo.

53:37.498 --> 53:38.791
Terima kasih.

53:39.792 --> 53:42.878
- Apa kata kita ucap selamat?
- Tunggu sekejap.

53:43.170 --> 53:44.255
Aduhai.

53:45.423 --> 53:47.258
